data.text:
Watch a preview of one of the songs and some robot banter from the show!

Join the robots Rabbit, Zer0, and The Spine from the band Steam Powered Giraffe in this 25 minute-long concert video that was filmed remotely during the Covid-19 Pandemic from 2020 to 2021.

Steam Powered Giraffe: Not Live and Not in Person! features three song performances alongside banter from the robots. This concert video also features a few outtakes and alternate takes of some scenes after the credits!

Your purchase also includes MP3s of the three songs from the show!

Features the songs:

Clockwork Vaudeville

Lyin' Awake

Honeybee

Starring:

Isabella Bunny Bennett (Rabbit)

Bryan Barbarin (Zer0)

David Michael Bennett (The Spine)

Lacey Johnson (Keyboardist/Guitarist)

Camille Penyak (Walter Worker/Dancer)

Chelsea Penyak (Walter Worker/Dancer)

Digital Video Version

This Digital Video Version gives you access to an online video of the concert!

Includes:

Unlimited access to an online video of the concert

(30 minutes long)

High-Quality MP3 downloads of the 3 song performances featured in the show; Clockwork Vaudeville, Lyin' Awake, and Honeybee

NOTE:Digital Videos are watchable on desktop computers and most mobile devices through our online store. If the advertisement video above plays for you on your device, the concert video will work too. An internet connection is required to watch these videos. Downloading the video is not available.

Concert video specs:

1920 x 1080 @ 24fps

(no closed captions or subtitles)

Digital Audio Files:

Each track will be delivered as a 320kpbs MP3 file. If you would like to download the album as FLAC or WAV, please purchase the album on our bandcamphere. You can download the entire album as either a ZIP file with all files compressed inside, or you may download the album's MP3 files individually. A JPG file of the album cover art is also included.
